{"Sid":0,"Did":124030,"Id":"512833","Title":"利澤簡永安宮格扇雕刻－大四季","ImageUrl":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-07-22/b6e8a148-a5e6-4d76-82a3-34598e62c3ee/collection/aafdfd48-59f3-4ac0-b15b-efd51966b0c6/109-her-pa-2207-202007191948235f142a911dda60.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-07-22/b6e8a148-a5e6-4d76-82a3-34598e62c3ee/collection/c2f51d5f-1c0b-4eb4-b3a6-44f46a994eeb/109-her-pa-2207-202007191948245f142a911dda61.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-07-22/b6e8a148-a5e6-4d76-82a3-34598e62c3ee/collection/23a7a7cf-9035-428b-8e71-80215bc36b64/109-her-pa-2207-202007191948245f142a911dda62.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-07-22/b6e8a148-a5e6-4d76-82a3-34598e62c3ee/collection/59badc85-ee8e-4ff5-85a4-2056684c2263/109-her-pa-2207-202007191948245f142a911dda63.jpg","IndexCode":"Culture_Place","CustomColumns":{"Description":"\n\n利澤簡永安宮中門兩側格扇餘塞板採傳統建築裝飾常見之「大四季」花卉主題之木透雕，置於小几之上的花瓶中插入四季花卉，除象徵季節外，也有四季平安、歲朝清供之意。龍邊大四季為春季與夏季之花卉。春季花卉為牡丹，四朵牡丹綻開程度不同，花開方向也不同，象徵「富貴平安」。下季花卉為蓮花，同樣可見數朵蓮花，綻開程度與花開方向也不相同，而中央直上生長的蓮花穿過破洞的蓮葉，頗具特色；右上方則刻飾以蓮蓬，以喻「連科」，與科舉功名的祈望有關。虎邊大四季為秋季與冬季之花卉。秋季花卉為菊花，其花瓣形狀清楚可辨，有側視滿開與半開菊花，亦有頂視滿開菊花，有「長壽」喻意。冬季花卉為梅花，梅花僅由五片花瓣構成，因此以數量較多的梅花配置，有「梅開五福」的吉祥寓意。利澤簡永安宮創建於清道光年間，今所見廟宇建築主體於1928-1930（昭和3-5）年間所重修，2006年被宜蘭縣政府公告指定為縣定古蹟。\n\n","Keyword_Rights_2":"CC BY / CC BY / CC BY / CC BY","Keyword_Des_Rights_2":"CC0","Keyword_Longitude":"121.823155","Keyword_Latitude":"24.666604","Original_Url":"https://cmsdb.culture.tw/place/58E3FE09-B720-4E82-8583-543EBBEC8FA8","Original_Identifier":"512833","Keyword_Subject_1":"民俗與宗教","alias":"","Keywords":"木雕 / 冬梅花 / 四季平安 / 春牡丹 / 秋菊花 / 夏蓮花 / 歲朝清供","historicalDates":"","LastUpdateTime":"2020/10/27 19:48:11","timelines":"","place":"","address":"宜蘭縣五結鄉利澤路26號","longitude":"121.823155","latitude":"24.666604","phone":"","Event":"","relationPeople":"","open":"0","free":"否","openTime":"","openTimeDescription":"","capacity":"","traffic":"","subjection":"","tag":"","situation":"","historicalDataBrief":"","historicalData":"","reference":"燦景古建築研究工作室（2008），《縣定古蹟利澤簡永安宮調查研究》。","writer":"葉永韶／蔡明志","createOrgName":"宜蘭縣政府文化局","source":"燦景古建築研究工作室（2008），《縣定古蹟利澤簡永安宮調查研究》。","Keyword_Rights_1":"","AllImages":"https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-07-22/b6e8a148-a5e6-4d76-82a3-34598e62c3ee/collectionOpen/73449e69-78b2-41cc-9f0e-3b49ec59aa42/109-her-pa-2207-re-202007191952055f142a911dda60.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-07-22/b6e8a148-a5e6-4d76-82a3-34598e62c3ee/collectionOpen/6749d885-5e0a-4e02-a774-be54967dc23f/109-her-pa-2207-re-202007191952055f142a911dda61.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-07-22/b6e8a148-a5e6-4d76-82a3-34598e62c3ee/collectionOpen/31cbd890-5d0b-40f2-a9fe-2a2ad5ac2b42/109-her-pa-2207-re-202007191952055f142a911dda62.jpg / https://dcm.s3.hicloud.net.tw/excel/place/2020-07-22/b6e8a148-a5e6-4d76-82a3-34598e62c3ee/collectionOpen/e92a2d04-6978-41f6-ad3d-f579ef7f1f1e/109-her-pa-2207-re-202007191952055f142a911dda63.jpg"}}